<L>__{interior mini mart morning}
<A>__{... where they crouch down the magazine rack. among the magazines is dog fancy with a picture of a chinese crested hairless on the cover and the headline: "emperor defends crown." parker peers over the top and out the window. parker's pov slowly, the lincoln cruises the street, bennie scanning the neighborhood for them.}
