<D>__{parker, you're only feeding the poor man's disease. buy him a healthy snack.}
<A>__{... just as the homeless guy reaches for the dollar and the slushee is knocked from his hand. we watch in slow motion as the slushee takes flight, the cap falling off and the sticky, cherry red mess fanning}
<B>__{out until...}
